text: Kandaura is a Gram Panchayat in Raebareli district in the state of Uttar Pradesh, India. The Pin Code of the Gram Panchayat is 229303 and there are 5 Village under Kandaura. Kandaura is also a Constituency under the district of Raebareli. Category:Villages in Raebareli district
title: Kandaura
